description: Regenerates the Primary/Secondary Keys to the NotificationHub Authorization Rule

authorization_rule_name.description: The connection string of the NotificationHub for the specified authorizationRule.

parameters.description: Parameters supplied to regenerate the NotificationHub Authorization Rule Key.

subscription_id.description: Gets subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

policykey.description: Name of the key that has to be regenerated for the Namespace/Notification Hub Authorization Rule. The value can be Primary Key/Secondary Key.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.
